Class UserRecord

  • java.lang.Object

  • public class UserRecord
extends Thing
    This class represents a small bit of data relevant to moderation logs such as banned users, accepted contributors, and moderators. Also used when using friends and blocked users.

    • Method Detail

      • getDate

        @JsonProperty
public java.util.Date getDate()
        This property has multiple meanings depending on the context. If this record is referring to a user being banned from or being added as a contributor to either the subreddit or the wiki, then this will return the date they were banned or added as a contributor. If this record is referring to a contributor or moderator, then this will return the date that the account was created. If this record is referring to a friend or a blocked user, then this will be the date that they were added as a friend or blocked.
        Returns:
        The date most relevant to this record
